6 th missile power.393 Iran designs and produces a variety of unmanned aerial vehicles UAVs and is considered a global leader and superpower in drone warfare and technology.394395396397398399400 It is one of the worlds five countries with cyberwarfare capabilities and is identified as one of the most active players in the international cyber arena.401402403 Following Russias purchase of Iranian drones during the invasion of Ukraine404405406407 in November 2023 the Islamic Republic of Iran Air Force IRIAF finalized arrangements to acquire Russian Sukhoi Su35 fighter jets Mil Mi28 attack helicopters air defence and missile systems.408409410411 The Iranian Navy has had joint exercises with Russia and China.412413414415416 Nuclear program Main article Nuclear program of Iran See also Nuclear facilities in Iran Views on the nuclear program of Iran and Joint Comprehensive Plan of Action Iran nuclear program dates back to the 19
50 s when it received technical assistance under the U.S. Atoms for Peace program.417 While this assistance ended with the Revolution Iran remained interested in nuclear technology so it revived the program and developed an extensive nuclear fuel cycle including sophisticated enrichment capabilities which became the subject of intense international negotiations and sanctions.418 Many countries have expressed concern that Iran could divert civilian nuclear technology into a weapons programme.419420421 On 14 July 2015 Iran and the P51 agreed to the Joint Comprehensive Plan on Action JCPOA aiming to end economic sanctions in exchange for Irans restriction in producing enriched uranium.422423 In 2018 however the United States withdrew from the deal under the Trump administration and intended to reimpose sanctions on Iran. This decision was met with resistance by Iran and the other members of the P
51.4 24425426427 A year later Iran began decreasing its compliance.428 By 2020 Iran announced that it would no longer observe any limit set by the agreement.429430 Progress since then has brought Iran to the nuclear threshold status.431432433 As of November 2023 Iran has uranium enriched to up to 60 fissile content close to weapon grade.434435436437 Some analysts already regard the country as a de facto nuclear power.438439440441 Regional influence Main articles Iranian influence in Lebanon Iranian intervention in the Syrian civil war and Iranian intervention in Iraq 20
